            <span class="mt-0.5 text-[var(--accent)]">&#10003;</span>
            <span>Destination content — structured guides, itinerary pages, "best for" comparison tables — is the highest-citability content format in travel.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
